														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1466890">
									

<p>Yoric's introduction of AWCY? is written as documents retrieved from a mole about the Foundation's investigation into their planned terrorist attack on Wall st.</p>
<p>It would be really hard for at least a few cells to not know about the foundation.</p>
<p>With that said there are probably cells that don't know about the Foundation per se, but the people ultimately in charge definitely would. How much information they would share with the rest would be an open question.</p>
<p>*edit*<br />
Should add that Yoric did specify that they didn't know about the Foundation before the Ossify Wall St. incident in that thread you linked. So I guess there is that.</p>

							</div>

								
